OL,3,CInflation no longer burns white hot -
OL,4,Cbut it's still glowing
OL,6,FThe rate rose to 2.6%, up from 2.3% in
OL,7,Fthe year to October - meaning the
OL,8,Flevel remains above the Bank of
OL,9,FEngland's target, as ITV News
OL,10,FEconomics Editor reports
OL,12,FThe headline annual rate edged up to
OL,13,F2.6% last month.
OL,15,FPut another way, prices across the UK
OL,16,Fin November were 2.6% higher than in
OL,17,FNovember a year ago.
OL,19,FOn the face of it, this is a setback.
