OL,3,CInflation no longer burns white hot -
OL,4,Cbut it's still glowing
OL,6,FIt's the second consecutive monthly
OL,7,Frise away from the Bank of England's
OL,8,F2% target (the rate at which price
OL,9,Frises are considered to be "stable")
OL,10,Fand inflation is now at its highest
OL,11,Flevel for six months.
OL,13,FBut perspective, please. Inflation was
OL,14,Frunning at 11% two years ago, there's
OL,15,Fno reason to fear we're heading back
OL,16,Fthere.
