OL,3,CInflation no longer burns white hot -
OL,4,Cbut it's still glowing
OL,6,FBut using what economists call "base
OL,7,Feffects" in this way can provide a
OL,8,Fmisleading picture of what is going on.
OL,10,FFor example, the price of petrol and
OL,11,Fdiesel helped to drive the headline
OL,12,Frate up, but that's because pump
OL,13,Fprices fell by less on an annual basis
OL,14,Fin November 2024 (-10.9 %) than they
OL,15,Fdid in October 2024 (13.7%). The price
OL,16,Fof petrol did rise to 134.8 pence/
OL,17,Flitre last month but a year ago it was
OL,18,F151 pence/litre.
