OL,3,CInflation no longer burns white hot -
OL,4,Cbut it's still glowing
OL,6,FYesterday, we learned that wage
OL,7,Finflation in the private sector is
OL,8,Frising at 5.4% a year - well above the
OL,9,Flevel the Bank of England considers to
OL,10,Fbe consistent with bringing inflation
OL,11,Fsustainably back to target.
OL,13,FMany businesses are also trying to
OL,14,Fwork out how to deal with the extra
OL,15,Fcosts imposed on them in the Budget in
OL,16,FOctober.
