OL,3,CInflation no longer burns white hot -
OL,4,Cbut it's still glowing
OL,6,FThe extent to which firms do each of
OL,7,Fthese things will determine what the
OL,8,FBank of England does next with
OL,9,Finterest rates.
OL,11,FIt's a tricky time for the Bank. Zero
OL,12,Feconomic growth and rising inflation
OL,13,Fare not a happy combination.
OL,15,FThe antidote to rising prices is
OL,16,Fhigher interest rates, the tonic for
OL,17,Fanaemic growth is lower interest
OL,18,Frates. What's a central bank to do?
OL,20,FVery little. At least, that's the view
OL,21,Fof investors.
